
    Original NES Game Genie codes created by:

      Tony Hedstrom   t_hedstrom@yahoo.com


   The Legend of Zelda

NOTE: To get to the cave described below, from the
starting point of the game, go up one screen, then go
left one screen.


AAVATTEZ
Buy the Large Shield for free (instead of $160) in the
cave just northwest of where you start the game.

AAVAYTGT
Buy Keys for free (instead of $100) in the cave just
northwest of where you start the game.

AAVEAVGL
Buy the Blue Candle for free (instead of $60) in the
cave just northwest of where you start the game.
